class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 09, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mea1665702595617.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mea1665702595617.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mea1665702595617.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mea1665702595617\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the URL where JavaScript files for dynamic server pages are located at\n      runtime.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mea1665702595617__topic_d144005e1_d144006e1_d144007e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mea1665702595617__p_d144008e1_d144009e1_d144010e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$JS_BASE_URL</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> } <var class=\"keyword varname\">URL</var></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mea1665702595617__section_mqq_qgn_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d769896e64\">Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mea1665702595617__p_d144014e1_d144015e1_d144016e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">URL</var>—relative path from the web\n            server root to the location of the DSP JavaScript files at runtime</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mea1665702595617__section_zt1_sgn_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d769896e75\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mea1665702595617__table_d17429e1_d17430e1_d17431e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">wasv.asn</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[WEB]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">../common/dspjs</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mea1665702595617__section_f25_5gn_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d769896e124\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mea1665702595617__p_d144023e1_d144024e1_d144025e1\">By default, Uniface expects to find a component's\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">.js</span> file, whether copied during deployment or generated\n            on-the-fly, in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">../common/dspjs</span> directory relative to the page's\n            base URL. For example, in the default installation, this would be:\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">http://localhost:8080/uniface/wrd/../common/dspjs</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mea1665702595617__p_d144026e1_d144027e1_d144028e1\">You use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$JS_BASE_URL</span> setting\n            to specify a different URL (relative or absolute) in your Uniface Server's assignment\n            file (<span class=\"ph filepath\">wasv.asn</span> in the standard installation).</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529872\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529872\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$JS_BASE_URL Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 09, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specify the URL where JavaScript files for dynamic server pages are located at runtime. $JS_BASE_URL { = } URL Values URL —relative path from the web server root to the location of the DSP JavaScript files at runtime Defaults Assignment file: wasv.asn Section: [WEB] Default value: ../common/dspjs Description By default, Uniface expects to find a component's .js file, whether copied during deployment or generated on-the-fly, in the ../common/dspjs directory relative to the page's base URL. For example, in the default installation, this would be: http://localhost:8080/uniface/wrd/../common/dspjs . You use the $JS_BASE_URL setting to specify a different URL (relative or absolute) in your Uniface Server's assignment file ( wasv.asn in the standard installation). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}